name: UPhysicalMaterialMask
doc: Physical material masks are used to map multiple physical materials to a single rendering material

MaskTexture: Mask input texture, square aspect ratio recommended. Recognized mask colors include: white, black, red, green, yellow, cyan, turquoise, and magenta.
UVChannelIndex: StaticMesh UV channel index to use when performing lookups with this mask.
AddressX: The addressing mode to use for the X axis.
AddressY: The addressing mode to use for the Y axis.
